tooltipText:
Deal $hit1$ and apply a debuff to the target. While the debuff is active, the target acquires 5 wound stacks per second that they are moving.

After 5 seconds, the target takes another $hit:Fighter_Rupture_EndHit$, plus 1% additional damage for each stack of wound it has, up to a maximum total of $hit:Fighter_Rupture_EndHit.max$
name: Fighter_Rupture
